metadata.name: Phoenix Rave 1/1
metadata.description:
This is a 1/1 special edition featuring the Phoenix that symbolises "Rebirth and Good Fortune".  

After paying for platform fees, all proceeds from this auction will go to 'Da Nang Hospital For Women And Children' and support the kids undergoing cancer treatment. 

Revenue generated from Phoenix Rave's YouTube will support this cause in perpetuity.
